OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FWords by ITV News West Country
OL,7,Fpresenter Sabet Choudhury
OL,9,F"I'm worried about going out" - those
OL,10,Fwere words I never expected to hear
OL,11,Ffrom my own father.
OL,13,FBut last summer as the violent anti-
OL,14,Fimmigration protests flared up around
OL,15,Fthe country, following the murder of
OL,16,Fthree little girls in Southport, I
OL,17,Fwatched this fearless retired surgeon
OL,18,Fbecome fearful for his safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
