OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FOver the course of a week as the
OL,7,Fprotests spread, many of them
OL,8,Freplicated scenes from the 1970's and
OL,9,F80's, as hate and rage turned into
OL,10,Fviolence.
OL,12,FOver the last three decades, as a
OL,13,Fjournalist, I have seen many protests
OL,14,Fand demonstrations turn into riots.
OL,15,FBut this time, it felt different, and
OL,16,Fmore menacing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
