OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FSeeing the images of right-wing groups
OL,7,Fand daubed graffiti telling asylum
OL,8,Fseekers being housed in hotels to "get
OL,9,Fout of England", even made me think,
OL,10,F"Am I Safe?".
OL,12,FSometimes I forget that scenes like
OL,13,Fthis playing out on our screens can
OL,14,Fmake even the most secure person of
OL,15,Fcolour feel like prey that needs to go
OL,16,Finto hiding.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
