OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FDuring that week there was a sense of
OL,7,Fdread, where and when, will the next
OL,8,Fprotest happen. Could it be on our
OL,9,Fdoorstep? Social media, as ever,
OL,10,Fplayed its part.
OL,12,FThis time in spreading disinformation,
OL,13,Fwhipping up the growing anti-immigrant
OL,14,Fsentiment, into a frenzy. The violent
OL,15,Fscenes that played in parts of the
OL,16,FWest Country and elsewhere in the UK,
OL,17,Fcame as a warning sign that all is not
OL,18,Fwell.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
