OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FFast forward a month after those
OL,7,Fviolence protests, I still sensed a
OL,8,Ffear in my father. A worry that there
OL,9,Fcould be a repeat of the racist
OL,10,Fsentiments he witnessed in the UK as a
OL,11,Fyounger man.
OL,13,FWas he isolated in his worry, or were
OL,14,Fthere others like him? I found my
OL,15,Fanswer amongst the Senegalese
OL,16,Fcommunity in Bristol's Stapleton Road.
OL,18,FWe gathered a group at a community
OL,19,Fcafe for a chat, that included adults
OL,20,Fwho have been in the UK for over 20
OL,21,Fyears, and children who were born here.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
