OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FThe conversation was for a TV piece,
OL,7,Fand what I heard was worrying.
OL,9,FThe children spoke of being scared
OL,10,Fthat they might be attacked, while the
OL,11,Fadults lived in fear and unable to
OL,12,Faccept that this felt like home
OL,13,Fanymore.
OL,15,FThis interview for me was the moment I
OL,16,Fdecided to explore this issue of how
OL,17,Fwe got to this place, where the
OL,18,Fcountry was so seemingly divided.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
