OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FA country where immigrants were seen
OL,7,Fas "freeloaders" and anyone who wanted
OL,8,Fto control our borders as "racists".
OL,10,FIn the months that followed I worked
OL,11,Fwith a team here at ITV News West
OL,12,FCountry to find an array of voices, to
OL,13,Ftake a temperature check of where
OL,14,Fthose often violent protests of 2024
OL,15,Fhave left us. Could they happen again
OL,16,Fand what needs to be done to make sure
OL,17,Fcommunities feel better heard.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
