OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FThe process of making the programme
OL,7,Fopened my eyes to a wide array of
OL,8,Fideas and views. Not least that this
OL,9,Fis a polarising subject with no real
OL,10,Fclear cut answer.
OL,12,FMy guests included a criminologist who
OL,13,Ftold me about the pain of facing
OL,14,Fracial hatred, and seeing scenes of
OL,15,Fviolence play out, like the riots of
OL,16,Fthe 80's where her uncle's shops were
OL,17,Fburned down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
