OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FI also heard from a self-employed
OL,7,Ftradesman who was given a two year
OL,8,Fprison sentence after he turned
OL,9,Fviolent during a anti-immigration
OL,10,Fprotest in Bristol.
OL,12,FAfter six months behind bars Dan Lock
OL,13,Fis out of prison on license, and
OL,14,Fsitting opposite me telling me his
OL,15,Fside of the story.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
