OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FIt's hard not to like Dan, he's polite
OL,7,Fand pleasant, certainly not the image
OL,8,Fof a protester that many people would
OL,9,Fimagine. I'm told he's someone who has
OL,10,Fnever been in trouble or in jail. So
OL,11,Fwhat happened?
OL,13,FFrom the moment we started the
OL,14,Finterview, he expressed his sorrow for
OL,15,Fturning violent during the protest
OL,16,Foutside a hotel housing asylum-seekers
OL,17,Fin Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
