OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FHe says he retaliated after being
OL,7,Fcalled a Nazi. "So I'm a racist,'cos
OL,8,FI'm white and I'm bald?" he says,
OL,9,Fwhile also pointing to the tattoos on
OL,10,Fhis arm.
OL,12,FHe also tells me how he firmly
OL,13,Fbelieves in "stopping the boats" and
OL,14,Fthat the country needs to cease
OL,15,Fspending "billions on housing illegal
OL,16,Fimmigrants" all the while his
OL,17,Fgrandparents' winter fuel allowance is
OL,18,Fbeing cut.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
