OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FHe ran into hiding while his mother
OL,7,Fand father were slaughtered.
OL,9,FEric is now awaiting his fate in this
OL,10,Fcountry. He's been left in limbo
OL,11,Funable to get a job and start a new
OL,12,Flife, while he waits for his asylum
OL,13,Fclaim to be processed, Eric is housed
OL,14,Fin a hotel. In 2024 he was in
OL,15,FTamworth, a place that became a target
OL,16,Fduring the protests.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
