OL,3,CHow my father's fear triggered an
OL,4,Cinvestigation into last summer's riots
OL,6,FThe process of making Disunited
OL,7,FBritain has been a labour of love, and
OL,8,Ffear.
OL,10,FI wasn't sure what answers this
OL,11,Fprocess could uncover. The possibility
OL,12,Fof a fractured nation unable to come
OL,13,Ftogether again, is frightening in
OL,14,Fitself, let alone the thought of that
OL,15,Fviolence playing out again.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
